c: 29
v: 10
t: "There are some people who say, ÂṀWe have iman in Allah,ÂṀ and then, when they suffer harm in AllahÂṀs cause, they take peopleÂṀs persecution for AllahÂṀs punishment; but if help comes from your Lord they say, ÂṀWe were with you.ÂṀ Does Allah not know best what is in every personÂṀs heart"